General.Name: Tombador Iron Ltd
General.Description: Tombador Iron Limited engages in the exploration of iron ore deposits in Brazil. It owns 100% of the Tombador iron ore project in Bahia State, Brazil. The company was formerly known as Resa Group Limited and changed its name to Tombador Iron Limited in 2020. Tombador Iron Limited was incorporated in 2004 and is based in Cottesloe, Australia.
